---
// Hero: light pink/beige bg, 3 iPhones left, right: headline, text, Book Repair (pink), Shop Accessories (outline)
---

<section id="hero" class="bg-brand-pink">
  <div class="mx-auto flex max-w-7xl flex-col items-center gap-12 px-4 py-16 md:flex-row md:items-center md:justify-between md:gap-12 md:py-24 lg:px-8">
    <div class="flex-1 flex justify-center md:order-1">
      <div class="relative h-72 w-64 sm:h-80 sm:w-72 md:h-96 md:w-80">
        <div class="absolute left-0 top-0 h-56 w-28 rounded-[1.75rem] border-[8px] border-copy-dark bg-copy-dark shadow-lg" style="transform: rotate(-8deg);">
          <div class="absolute inset-1.5 rounded-[1.2rem] bg-gradient-to-br from-violet-500 via-fuchsia-500 to-pink-500" />
          <div class="absolute top-3 left-1/2 h-4 w-14 -translate-x-1/2 rounded-full bg-black/40" />
        </div>
        <div class="absolute left-12 top-4 h-52 w-26 rounded-[1.75rem] border-[8px] border-amber-200 bg-amber-100 shadow-lg" style="transform: rotate(-4deg);">
          <div class="absolute inset-1.5 rounded-[1.2rem] bg-gradient-to-br from-rose-400 to-pink-400" />
          <div class="absolute top-3 left-1/2 h-4 w-12 -translate-x-1/2 rounded-full bg-black/30" />
        </div>
        <div class="absolute left-24 top-8 h-48 w-24 rounded-[1.5rem] border-[6px] border-slate-300 bg-slate-200 shadow-lg" style="transform: rotate(2deg);">
          <div class="absolute inset-1 rounded-[1rem] bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-400 via-purple-400 to-pink-400" />
          <div class="absolute top-2 left-1/2 h-3 w-10 -translate-x-1/2 rounded-full bg-black/30" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="flex-1 md:order-2 md:pl-4">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-semibold leading-tight tracking-tight text-copy-dark sm:text-5xl lg:text-[3.25rem]">
        Discover the Convenience of Professional
      </h1>
      <p class="mt-6 max-w-lg text-base text-copy-medium leading-relaxed">
        Upgrade Your Phone's Protection with Armor Film and Discover a Wide Selection of Accessories to Personalize Your Device.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap gap-4">
        <a href="#contact" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-accent-pink px-8 py-3.5 text-base font-medium text-white hover:opacity-90 transition-opacity">
          Book Repair
        </a>
        <a href="#products" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-lg border-2 border-copy-dark bg-transparent px-8 py-3.5 text-base font-medium text-copy-dark hover:bg-copy-dark hover:text-white transition-colors">
          Shop Accessories
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
